DEFAULT_MACRO _WB_BYPASS_TERMINATION No
FACTORY_DEF * TeeFactory FACTORY_NAME XMLFragmenter_<Rejected> INPUT FEATURE_TYPE XMLFragmenter_<REJECTED>  NO_LOGGING   OUTPUT FAILED FEATURE_TYPE * @Abort(ENCODED, XMLFragmenter<space>output<space>a<space><lt>Rejected<gt><space>feature.<space><space>To<space>continue<space>translation<space>when<space>features<space>are<space>rejected<comma><space>change<space><apos>Workspace<space>Parameters<apos><space><gt><space>Log<space>and<space>Troubleshoot<space><gt><space><apos>Rejected<space>Feature<space>Handling<apos><space>to<space><apos>Continue<space>Translation<apos>)
